  19 Jan 2009; Ben de Groot <yngwin@gentoo.org>
  vdr-graphtft-0.1.21_alpha.ebuild:
  Specifying qt-gui:4 as dep, as generic x11-libs/qt is certainly not right,
  and split Qt 4.4.2 is going stable

